OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 01 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1999FBBC Knowledge begins
OL,7,Fbroadcasting on digital platforms. It
OL,8,Foffered a mix of educational programmes
OL,9,Fand documentaries. When the BBC's
OL,10,Fdigital programme was launched at
OL,11,FTelevision Centre in London by
OL,12,Fdirector-general Sir John Birt on 21st
OL,13,FSeptember 1998, the planned education
OL,14,Fand information channel was referred to
OL,15,Fas BBC Learning. BBC Knowledge closed
OL,16,Fon 2nd March 2002 and was replaced by
OL,17,FBBC Four.
